tdoe_error_description: Session Begin Date must be within the school year.
Session End Date must be within the school year.
Session Begin Date must be less than or equal to End Date.
Sections only get one of Honors, Statewide Dual Credit, Local Dual Credit, Dual Enrollment.
Sections only get one of F or S or T.
Sections that are not Pull Out must have a meeting time duration.
Sections must have an educational_environment_type.
Class Periods cannot have more than one meeting time.
Class Periods must have a positive meeting time duration.
Bell Schedules must have dates.
Date Entered US cannot be missing for an immigrant student.
Date Entered US must exist for students with English Language Background code L,W,1,2,3,4,F,N.
Native Language must exist for students.
Race must exist for students.
Cohort Year must exist for Students with instructional grade greater than 8.
Student Characteristics End Date must be greater than or equal to Begin Date.
Student cannot have overlapping Student Characteristics records for the same characteristics.
Entry Date must be within the school year.
Withdrawal Date must be within the school year.
Withdrawal Date must be greater than or equal to Entry Date.
No primary enrollment exists but secondary enrollment does exist.
Student cannot have overlapping Primary enrollments.
Student cannot have more than one School Association with Enrollment Reason Code of E or E1 in a single school year.
Student cannot have TR Enrollment Reason Code if there is not existing E or E1 at a different school in a single school year.
Student cannot have more than one enrollment reason code in a single school year.
Homeless students must have homeless primary nighttime residence.
Discipline Date must fall on a School Day.
Discipline Action Length must fall on a School Day.
Actual Discipline Action Length must fall on a School Day.
Discipline Incident Date cannot be after Discipline Action Date.
Discipline Actions for a Student are not allowed to overlap.
Student Standard Day must be within enrollment period.
Student attendance/absence must be within enrollment period.
Student Section Begin Date must be within the school year.
Student Section End Date must be within the school year.
Student Section Begin Date must be within the enrollment period.
Student Academic Record Completion Date is not within the school year.
Final Letter Grade must be an acceptable value.
Final Numeric Grade must be an acceptable value.
